Package: smoothscale
Type: Package
Title: Smooth Counts and Scale to Benchmarks
Version: 0.1.0
Author: John Bryant
Maintainer: John Bryant <john@bayesiandemography.com>
Description: Functions for basic small area estimate that
    (i) smooth out sampling variation and (ii) scale local-level
    results to match national-level benchmarks.
